export const capitalizeFirstLetter = ([first, ...rest]: string) => first.toUpperCase() + rest.join('').toLowerCase();

export const capitalizeSentence = (words: string) =>
  words
    .split(' ')
    .map((word) => capitalizeFirstLetter(word))
    .join(' ');
